        <div class="timeline-right">
          <h3 class="timeline-title font-display">IT Intern</h3>
          <p class="timeline-company accent-purple">Guardian Life Insurance Ltd</p>
          <p class="timeline-desc">Rebuilding existing platforms with new technologies such as NextJS and React with comprehensive testing.</p>
        </div>
