        <span class="post-date font-mono">Oct 14, 2025</span>
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://medium.com/@akifzahin/lessons-ive-learned-standing-in-the-middle-of-loss-and-death-9697c3fdb4fa"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="post-item"
