  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <section class="section" id="about">
    <p class="section-label">About</p>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <p class="about-text">
        Born and raised in Dhaka, I've loved spending time tinkering with new
        technology, all types of games and musical instruments whenever I could.
        Now having studied Computer Science, I love building software that focus
        on integrating AI with full-stack applications in an eco-friendly and
        efficient manner.
        <br />PS: I also have <span class="accent-purple">two lovely cats.</span
        > Here's a picture of them.
      </p>
      <img src="/images/cats.jpg" alt="My two cats" class="cat-img" />
    </div>
  </section>

